OL,3,CMan charged with murder after 'loving
OL,4,Cand devoted' man killed in hit-and-run
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Fafter a 29-year-old man was killed in
OL,8,Fa hit-and-run in Wolverhampton.
OL,10,FRyan Griffiths was seriously injured
OL,11,Fwhen he was hit by a car in Burleigh
OL,12,FRoad in Merridale just before 9pm on
OL,13,FAugust 21 and died in hospital two
OL,14,Fdays later.
OL,16,FAden Wright, 26, has been charged with
OL,17,FMr Griffiths' murder and appeared at
OL,18,FWolverhampton Magistrates' Court on
OL,19,FWednesday (28 August).
